---
---
<section class="section-vast-experience">
  <div class="container vast-container">
    <div class="vast-left">
      <div class="vast-image-wrap">
        <img src="/assets/carver-law-homepage-about-section-min.jpg" alt="Thomas Carver with Award Plaques" />
      </div>
      <div class="vast-cta">
        <a href="tel:4173501172" class="btn btn-vast-cta">+ FREE CONSULTATION</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="vast-content">
      <p class="vast-eyebrow">VAST EXPERIENCE, UNMATCHED RESULTS</p>
      
      <div class="experience-list">
        <div class="experience-item">
          <span class="vast-plus-icon">+</span>
          <div class="vast-item-text">
            <h3>50+ YEARS OF EXCELLENCE</h3>
            <p>Few can match Thomas Carver's track record of legal excellence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-item">
          <span class="vast-plus-icon">+</span>
          <div class="vast-item-text">
            <h3>1,000+ SATISFIED CLIENTS</h3>
            <p>Consistently delivering the best possible outcomes for his clients in courts statewide.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-item">
          <span class="vast-plus-icon">+</span>
          <div class="vast-item-text">
            <h3>300+ FEDERAL CASES</h3>
            <p>One of the most experienced federal litigators in Springfield and the State of Missouri.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-vast-experience {
    background-color: #1a2c38 !important; /* Force primary dark teal */
    padding: 5rem 0 8rem; /* Reduced top padding to create overhang space */
    color: #ffffff !important;
    position: relative;
  }

  .vast-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 480px 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .vast-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: -8rem; /* Pull image up past the section padding for overhang */
  }

  .vast-image-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .vast-image-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .btn-vast-cta {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 380px;
    height: 70px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: #bed05c !important; /* Lime green */
    color: #1a2c38 !important;
    border-radius: 21px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-vast-cta:hover {
    background: #a9ba4a !important;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .vast-content {
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .vast-eyebrow {
    color: #bed05c !important; /* Lime green */
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .experience-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .experience-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .vast-plus-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 0.8;
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-top: -5px;
  }

  .vast-item-text h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .vast-item-text p {
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) !important;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .vast-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    .vast-left {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .vast-eyebrow {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
